  <title>Sudo-&sudo-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The Sudo package allows a system administrator to give certain users (or
      groups of users) the ability to run some (or all) commands as <systemitem
      class="username">root</systemitem> or another user while logging the
      commands and arguments.
    </para>

